Title: Unmodern Jewelry
Description:
Some of the local Jewelcrafters are looking to study examples of the Zaqali tribes adornments.

Given they are currently attacking my home, we may take advantage of the situation.

I thought you might take them violently, yes?

Argonax waits once you have collected them.
ObjectivesCompletionText: Deliver the supplies to Argonax in the Emerald Dream.

Objectives.Text: Complete the events of "Enter the Dream"
